code: @Before public void setup() {     this.binder = new Binder(this.sources).     this.name = ConfigurationPropertyName.of("foo"). }

@Test public void bindToPackagePrivateClassShouldBindToInstance() {     MockConfigurationPropertySource source = new MockConfigurationPropertySource().     source.put("foo.bar", "999").     this.sources.add(source).     ExamplePackagePrivateBean bean = this.binder.bind(this.name, Bindable.of(ExamplePackagePrivateBean.class)).get().     assertThat(bean.getBar()).isEqualTo(999). }
